ANSIBLE - AUTHENTICATION

GROUP_VARS 

This document covers the following items:
  1 Understanding group_vars
  2 Set the authentication user

1 Understanding group_vars 
  The group_vars directory is designed to set specific variables that can be used as standard for all playbooks.

2 Set the authentication user
  In order to allow the user iac to run playbooks on remote hosts, the following line was added into the file gorup_vars/all
  ansible_ssh_user: svc_ansible

References:  
https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/user_guide/intro_inventory.html
